sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Main as Main Thread
    participant Dir as Director
    participant Bus as AnimationBus
    participant Stage as StageManager
    participant Hero as Hero Section
    participant Work as Work Section
    participant Bio as Biography Section
    participant Seq as LandingSequence

    Note over Main: DOMContentLoaded fires
    Main->>+Dir: new Director()

    rect rgb(255, 235, 205)
    Note over Dir: Phase 1 Event Bus Creation
    Dir->>+Bus: new AnimationBus()
    Bus-->>-Dir: bus instance
    Note right of Dir: Central event coordinator<br/>for all animations
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
    Note over Dir: Phase 2 Stage Setup
    Dir->>+Stage: new StageManager()
    Stage->>Stage: Initialize ScrollSmoother
    Stage->>Stage: Add background video
    Stage->>Stage: Setup visual effects
    Stage-->>-Dir: stage instance
    Dir->>Stage: getSmoother()
    Stage-->>Dir: smoother or null
    Note right of Dir: Scroll smoothing and<br/>visual effects controller
    end

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
    Note over Dir: Phase 3 Section Controllers
    Dir->>+Hero: new Hero(bus, smoother)
    Hero->>Hero: super('main-header', bus, smoother)
    Hero->>Hero: createIntro() - TextParty.roll
    Hero->>Hero: createScrollTriggers() - reversed roll
    Hero-->>-Dir: hero instance

    Dir->>+Work: new Work(bus, smoother)
    Work->>Work: super('work', bus, smoother)
    Work->>Work: createIntro() - fade animation
    Work->>Work: createScrollTriggers() - printer marks
    Work-->>-Dir: work instance

    Dir->>+Bio: new Biography(bus, smoother)
    Bio->>Bio: super('biography', bus, smoother)
    Bio->>Bio: createIntro() - fade animation
    Bio->>Bio: createScrollTriggers() - list reveals
    Bio-->>-Dir: biography instance
    Note right of Dir: All section controllers<br/>ready with paused timelines
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
    Note over Dir: Phase 4 Choreography Setup
    Dir->>+Seq: new LandingSequence(bus, sections)
    Seq->>Seq: setupSequence()
    Seq->>Bus: on('section:hero:intro:complete', ...)
    Seq->>Bus: on('section:hero:scroll:exit', ...)
    Seq->>Bus: on('section:work:intro:complete', ...)
    Note over Seq: Event listeners define<br/>animation flow
    Seq-->>-Dir: sequence instance
    Note right of Dir: Choreography coordinator<br/>configured
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 230)
    Note over Dir: Phase 5 Start Sequence
    Dir->>+Seq: start()
    Seq->>Hero: playIntro()
    activate Hero
    Note over Hero: TextParty.roll begins
    Hero->>Bus: emit('section:hero:intro:start')
    Bus-->>Seq: event received
    Hero->>Hero: timeline.play()
    Note over Hero: Animation plays
    Hero->>Bus: emit('section:hero:intro:complete')
    Bus-->>Seq: event received
    Seq->>Work: playIntro() (via event handler)
    activate Work
    Note over Work: Work section fade begins
    deactivate Hero
    deactivate Work
    deactivate Seq
    end

    Dir-->>-Main: Constructor complete
    Note over Main,Dir: window.director available<br/>Animation sequence running